title: Add V3 SGX Program to solana.js
body:
**Javascript**
- add sgx program generate-client script
- generate sgx types to new separate namespace
- add aggregatorTeeSaveResult
- add oracleTeeHeartbeat
- add sgx program accounts and ixns (addMrEnclave, removeMrEnclave)
- add new parameters to queueSetConfig
- add new parameters to programSetConfig

Rust
- add new accounts to switchboard-v2
- MAYBE: rename crate to switchboard-solana

title: chore: migrated devnet program to same pubkey as mainnet
body:
The Switchboard program now uses the same pubkey for mainnet and devnet, `SW1TCH7qEPTdLsDHRgPuMQjbQxKdH2aBStViMFnt64f`.

This reduces the need to use a feature flag when integrating the rust crate and makes the program more manageable.
